This project includes or is informed by:

1. ArduinoJson by Benoit Blanchon
   Licensed under the MIT License
   https://github.com/bblanchon/ArduinoJson

2. NordicSemiconductor bluetooth-numbers-database
   Licensed under the Nordic 5-Clause License
   https://github.com/NordicSemiconductor/bluetooth-numbers-database

3. Detection logic informed by:
   - glass-detect (sh4d0wm45k) — ESP32 smart glasses detector
   - banrays (NullPxl) — wearable glasses detector
   - ouispy-detector (colonelpanichacks) — BLE OUI scanner

BLE Company IDs from Bluetooth SIG Assigned Numbers registry:
  https://www.bluetooth.com/specifications/assigned-numbers/

OUI prefixes from IEEE MA-L registry and field captures.
